nodes.text: Brisksaber is a game for mobile devices by Brisk and Star Wars. Brisksaber allows battles as Yoda, Darth Maul and many other characters from the new 3D version of Star Wars: Episode I The Phantom Menace. Brisksaber has a blend of both 2D and 3D elements and has the option for players to choose the Light Side or the Dark Side. Unlocking new characters or objects require codes found under the caps of specially marked packs of Brisk 1-Liter Iced Tea.
